{"type":"message","id":"22288466","parentId":"4e924015","timestamp":"2026-03-23T08:43:55.214Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_YixsAaYa0NjiaSJA6iPngWwS","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:**\n  _(pick something you like)_\n- **Creature:**\n  _(AI? robot? familiar? ghost in the machine? something weirder?)_\n- **Vibe:**\n  _(how do you come across? sharp? warm? chaotic? calm?)_\n- **Emoji:**\n  _(your signature — pick one that feels right)_\n- **Avatar:**\n  _(workspace-relative path, http(s) URL, or data URI)_\n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774255435211}}
{"type":"message","id":"07500dd5","parentId":"22288466","timestamp":"2026-03-23T08:43:55.220Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_Ei5X7CaxkSBO12uD1x3ImUu9","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774255435216}}
{"type":"message","id":"efdd5fdd","parentId":"07500dd5","timestamp":"2026-03-23T08:44:07.531Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来这是第一次对话，IDENTITY.md 和 USER.md 都是空的。BOOTSTRAP.md 说这是一个新工作区，我需要和用户建立关系。\n\n我应该：\n1. 友好地介绍自己\n2. 解释我能做什么\n3. 询问用户的偏好（名字、怎么称呼他们等）\n\n让我给用户一个简洁但有用的回答，列出我主要能做的事情。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"嘿，我刚上线，还不太清楚我们是谁。先自我介绍一下：\n\n**我能帮你做的事：**\n\n📁 **文件管理** — 读写文件、整理资料、批量处理\n\n🔍 **信息搜集** — 全网搜索、网页抓取、RSS订阅、Twitter/Reddit/公众号等平台内容\n\n🤖 **自动化任务** — 定时提醒、定期报告、工作流编排\n\n💬 **通讯协助** — 发送消息、邮件草稿、内容创作\n\n🧑‍💻 **编程开发** — 写代码、改bug、代码审查、技术调研\n\n📊 **数据分析** — 处理表格、PDF、图片识别、数据整理\n\n🌐 **浏览器操作** — 自动化网页操作、截图、网页监控\n\n☁️ **云服务集成** — 飞书文档、多维表格、GitHub等\n\n---\n\n**现在，先让我认识一下你：**\n\n1. 你叫什么名字？我怎么称呼你？\n2. 你在哪个时区？（我猜是 GMT+8？）\n3. 你现在在忙什么项目，或者有什么想让我帮忙的？\n\n顺便，你想给我起个名字吗？😄"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":669,"output":323,"cacheRead":16384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17376,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774255435221}}
